</p></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-401EC7B6-28C5-4EB0-89A0-35EB13480638" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Behavior of the APSU status led</title><fig id="GUID-D0CF1838-377F-4E1A-A1C4-25F29A326246" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-B0BB2EB9-F2D3-4204-964A-0D0F766DE776-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-B0BB2EB9-F2D3-4204-964A-0D0F766DE776-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-2623D5A8-CD30-47AA-9847-1B2F0868BF48" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-CF9FE46B-BB0E-4122-BBD8-BDB2C1D39FD8-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-CF9FE46B-BB0E-4122-BBD8-BDB2C1D39FD8-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">LED basic diagnostics using flash codes: 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Permanent OFF</b> 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">No supply or internal hardware error. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Check supply, or replace the sensor. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Permanent ON</b> 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Internal hardware or software error, or a failed a self test. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">50 ms ON, 950 ms OFF</b> 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Sensor operating, but no serial connection during the last 5 sec. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">0.5 sec ON, 0.5 sec OFF</b> 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Sensor operating, and there is serial communication using the SRXS protocol. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">0.5 sec ON, 2.5 sec OFF</b> 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">Self test has passed 
</p></li></ul><p class="- topic/p ">Self test failed or defect board: 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">No blinking code, but LED is off or on. 
</p></section></conbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-BDCCF1E8-2922-4DF4-8281-9C54E2F3A962.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>Component locator</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
